    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/b41a68ea86d812dd6ed328a3098077b1.poster.avif?t=1761573164\" width=1170 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/b41a68ea86d812dd6ed328a3098077b1.webm?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/b41a68ea86d812dd6ed328a3098077b1.mp4?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A breathtaking metamorphosis awaits as you guide Venya through a world overcome by darkness. Use her shapeshifting powers to restore peace to a land that has gone without, for far too long.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the demo now for a first glimpse of Eden’s wonders!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Morph &amp; Traverse</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch seamlessly from human to wolf, raccoon, and raven. Each form offers unique traversal and combat mechanics. Glide like a raven through misty canopies, pounce like a wolf across beautiful landscapes, change into a raccoon to slip through tight ruins, and strike like a human with precision. Every form reveals new paths, puzzles, and secrets tucked across Eden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/04298cda3a7578991a5df8d2a1df84c6.poster.avif?t=1761573164\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/04298cda3a7578991a5df8d2a1df84c6.webm?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/04298cda3a7578991a5df8d2a1df84c6.mp4?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fluid form-blending Battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master an intricate combo system that blends attacks from different forms. Chain a raccoon’s nimble strikes into a wolf’s feral fury, then follow up with a human’s finishing blow. Master the flow of combat and help restore peace to the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/adeae62f68fbbd662794eda58aaf1f7b.poster.avif?t=1761573164\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/adeae62f68fbbd662794eda58aaf1f7b.webm?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/adeae62f68fbbd662794eda58aaf1f7b.mp4?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>From Blight to Bloom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies and conquer each boss to witness a corrupted area return to its natural beauty. Every victory restores a piece of Eden and reinforces the bond between inner peace and external hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/af47a4f39464d6698c38ad5d17c52661.poster.avif?t=1761573164\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/af47a4f39464d6698c38ad5d17c52661.webm?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059410/extras/af47a4f39464d6698c38ad5d17c52661.mp4?t=1761573164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Praised in early previews for its “soul-kindling environments” and “innovative multi-form combat system”, <i>Edenfall</i> is already turning heads among action-adventure and narrative fans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
